Description: The HCLS Knowledge Base at DERI is a Virtuoso-based triplestore containing information relevant to life science- medicine and health care. It contains RDF/OWL data that was generated by current and previous participants of the W3C Semantic Web for Health Care and Life Science Interest Group. A major part of the HCLS Knowledge Base is comprised of a mirror of the Neurocommons Knowledge Base maintained by Science Commons.Documentation can be found at http://www.w3.org/wiki/HCLSIG_BioRDF_Subgroup/DERI_HCLS_KB
